#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-15-ipad-keyboard-tips.rst:8
msgid "iPadでのキーボード操作を快適にする工夫"
msgstr "Tips to make keyboard operations more comfortable on the iPad"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-15-ipad-keyboard-tips.rst:10
msgid ""
"普段Windowsで作業している人がiPadにキーボードをつないで本格作業をしたい場合、キー配列の違いやショートカット操作のギャップに戸惑うことがあります。"
" この記事では、iPadでの作業効率を高めるための修飾キーの入れ替え方法と、覚えておくと便利なキー操作をまとめました。"
msgstr ""
"If you normally work on Windows and want to connect a keyboard to your iPad "
"and do some serious work, you may be confused by the differences in key "
"layouts and gaps in shortcut operations. In this article, we have summarized"
" how to replace modifier keys to increase work efficiency on the iPad, and "
"useful key operations to remember."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-15-ipad-keyboard-tips.rst:13
msgid "キーボードの違いに戸惑っている方や、vi操作やターミナル作業をiPadで快適に行いたい方の参考になれば幸いです。"
msgstr ""
"I hope this will be helpful for those who are confused about the differences"
" in keyboards, or those who want to comfortably operate vi and terminal work"
" on an iPad."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-15-ipad-keyboard-tips.rst:17
msgid "目次"
msgstr "table of contents"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-15-ipad-keyboard-tips.rst:20
msgid "修飾キーの入れ替えでWindows感覚に近づける"
msgstr "Get closer to the Windows feel by replacing modifier keys"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-15-ipad-keyboard-tips.rst:22
msgid ""
"iPadでは、CapsLockキーとCtrlキーの物理的位置がWindowsと異なるため、ショートカットが非常に押しにくく感じます。 "
"しかし、以下の手順で修飾キーを入れ替えることができ、**Windowsに近い操作感に調整可能** です。"
msgstr ""
"On iPad, the physical positions of the CapsLock and Ctrl keys are different "
"from Windows, so shortcuts feel very difficult to press. However, you can "
"replace the modifier keys by following the steps below, and you can adjust "
"the operation feel to be similar to Windows."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-15-ipad-keyboard-tips.rst:29
msgid "ここで、以下のように割り当てを変更するのがおすすめです："
msgstr "At this point, we recommend changing the assignments as follows:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-15-ipad-keyboard-tips.rst:31
msgid "Caps Lock → Control"
msgstr "Caps Lock → Control"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-15-ipad-keyboard-tips.rst:32
msgid "Control → Caps Lock（使わないなら「なし」にしても可）"
msgstr "Control → Caps Lock (If you don't use it, you can set it to \"None\")"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-15-ipad-keyboard-tips.rst:35
msgid "vi操作に便利な「ESC」キーの代替として「Ctrl + [」を使う"
msgstr ""
"Use \"Ctrl + [\" as an alternative to \"ESC\" key, which is convenient for "
"vi operations"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-15-ipad-keyboard-tips.rst:37
msgid ""
"iPadではESCキーが押しづらい、または存在しないキーボードもあります。 その代わりとして、**Ctrl + [** "
"を使えばVimでESCと同じ効果が得られます。"
msgstr ""
"On some iPad keyboards, the ESC key is difficult to press or doesn't exist. "
"Alternatively, use **Ctrl + [** to have the same effect as ESC in Vim."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-15-ipad-keyboard-tips.rst:40
msgid "これはVimユーザーにとって定番の代替操作であり、iPadなどの制限環境下でも非常に有効です。"
msgstr ""
"This is a classic alternative for Vim users, and is very useful even in "
"restricted environments such as the iPad."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-15-ipad-keyboard-tips.rst:43
msgid "iPadOSでの便利なショートカット操作一覧"
msgstr "List of useful shortcut operations on iPadOS"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-15-ipad-keyboard-tips.rst:45
msgid "iPad独自の操作もあります。Globeキー（地球儀キー）と組み合わせたショートカットで、多くのiPad操作が可能です。"
msgstr ""
"There are also operations unique to the iPad. Many iPad operations can be "
"performed using shortcuts combined with the Globe key."

